LESSON 6: Time Intelligence — Part 1
(DATEADD, SAMEPERIODLASTYEAR, PREVIOUSMONTH, LASTN Periods)

DATEADD(-3 MONTH) → only the month exactly 3 months back (e.g., April → January)

DATESINPERIOD(-3 MONTH) → last 3 months window combined (e.g., Apr+Mar+Feb)

Rolling_3_Months =
CALCULATE(
    [Total Sales],
    DATESINPERIOD(
        'Date'[Date],
        MAX('Date'[Date]),   -- current date context (April)
        -3,
        MONTH
    )
)
